Adult.description: Sagebrush Sparrows have a gray head and white eyering whereas adult Black-throated Sparrows have a bold white eyebrow and extensive black throat.
Bell's Sparrows have a gray head and white eyering, whereas adult Black-throated Sparrows have a bold white eyebrow and extensive black throat.

Breeding male.description: The Black-chinned Sparrow has a gray belly, whereas the Black-throated Sparrow has a whitish belly. Black-chinned also lacks the Black-throated's strongly striped face.
